# Minecraft Project Wizard – Project Overview

## Project Type
- **Framework**: Next.js (App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui (radix-nova style)

## Project Structure
- **Web App**: [web/](mdc:web/) – Next.js wizard
- **Template**: [template/](mdc:template/) – Gradle project templates (single/multi)
- **App Directory**: [web/src/app/](mdc:web/src/app/) – Next.js App Router
- **Components**: [web/src/components/](mdc:web/src/components/) – Reusable components
- **Wizard**: [web/src/components/wizard/](mdc:web/src/components/wizard/) – Main wizard form
- **Lib**: [web/src/lib/](mdc:web/src/lib/) – Utilities, templates, wizard logic

## Key Technologies
- Next.js with App Router
- TypeScript for type safety
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- shadcn/ui (Radix UI + Tailwind)
- JSZip for client-side ZIP generation
- Lucide React for icons

## Design Reference
- **Theme**: KMP JetBrains style (kmp.jetbrains.com) – dark theme, gold accent (#f0c45a)
- **Font**: JetBrains Mono
- **Colors**: #1e1e1e background, #252526 elevated, #f0c45a primary
